":"屌你老尾 讀多兩年書嗎識囉"},{"pid":"07f9d6283a92f90c8b01d09dc03b5c4c8a5d8bba","tid":359174,"uid":38528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有無人知點解要係壓水堆要將中子減速？</blockquote><br />\n唔減速咪核爆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152060dcc2f0ab1decec8c9d08f84349924294e0","tid":359174,"uid":69742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有無人知點解要係壓水堆要將中子減速？</blockquote><br />\n唔減速咪核爆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwrong"},{"pid":"8a8826238ff100af6c22bb4a6a1b808a0e5e4b48","tid":359174,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"慢啲易中啲"},{"pid":"f2237a88a7dd7a61f3a13eb4c85575f26ae6508b","tid":359174,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"做 neutron 好似係用 proton gun 打 beryllium proton gun 就係用電場加速 proton<br />\n<br />\nNeutron要用 moderator 減速，如果唔係 U235 唔吸<br />\n<br />\n放低好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a44d64cc179c946326dfc195bc82f7208d3a5b2","tid":359174,"uid":42250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"做 neutron 好似係用 proton gun 打 beryllium<br />\n<br />\nproton gun 就係用電場加速 proton<br />\n<br />\nNeutron要用 moderator 減速，如果唔係 U235 唔吸<br />\n<br />\n放低好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4311e0d4c2e66aefaee62bdcea468273aa8485","tid":359174,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"講一講返成個principle先<br />\nU-235佢係用黎製造能源(核電站)既通常用concentration 3%既<br />\n越高concentration佢個colliding chance 就越高<br />\n姐係會影響佢chain reaction既發生機率<br />\n*假設有一間房 ,concentration 就等於入面有幾多人 越多人係入面，咁大家膊頭撞膊頭機率就越大 姐係個chain reaction發生機率就越大<br />\n<br />\n重水既用途係用黎減慢speed of fast moving neutron,減慢佢個speed既目的就係為左比佢有機會同U-235發生反應 太快佢就會撞開左 咁就冇反應"},{"pid":"eedc456866418764b390808ffee2c23175a07a75","tid":359174,"uid":78678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講一講返成個principle先<br />\nU-235佢係用黎製造能源(核電站)既通常用concentration 3%既<br />\n越高concentration佢個colliding chance 就越高<br />\n姐係會影響佢chain reaction既發生機率<br />\n*假設有一間房 ,concentration 就等於入面有幾多人 越多人係入面，咁大家膊頭撞膊頭機率就越大 姐係個chain reaction發生機率就越大<br />\n<br />\n重水既用途係用黎減慢speed of fast moving neutron,減慢佢個speed既目的就係為左比佢有機會同U-235發生反應 太快佢就會撞開左 咁就冇反應</blockquote><br />\n其實要睇cross section"},{"pid":"89915531b869100e62f02299511b201fc4d64296","tid":359174,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Uranium 本身已經係唔穩定<br />\n自然breakdown 個陣會釋放d neutron出黎<br />\n放個d neutron又撞散其他uranium<br />\n一路重複 過程產生熱力同輻射</blockquote><br />\n咁即係放係到佢自己會核分裂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />uranium-235 濃度好似over 3% 已經會有chain reaction<br />\n法國有個鈾礦，先天已經夠高concentration﹐你可以當係天然的反應堆"},{"pid":"3f5b537757b949d5b2b6788fba0987e992c67465","tid":359174,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"既然佢會自己有reaction<br />\n咁原材料會點儲存?<br />\n利伸:完全唔識"},{"pid":"456b0d74cb1eb2220b88ae58032edb4e95dd8420","tid":359174,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkyyfc.org.hk/image/tricks/thps1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkyyfc.org.hk%2Fimage%2Ftricks%2Fthps1.gif&h=69271c1e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}